<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" version="2.0"><channel><title>The Far Side - Daily Dose - The Far Side</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/</link><description>Daily The Far Side - Daily Dose comic strip by Gary Larson from The Far Side</description><atom:link href="https://comiccaster.xyz/feeds/farside-daily.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><category>The Far Side</category><category>Comic Strips</category><docs>http://www.rssboard.org/rss-specification</docs><generator>python-feedgen</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 24 Jul 2026 08:21:43 +0000</lastBuildDate><ttl>1440</ttl><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-07-24 #5</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/24/4</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F26ca507002820138d7bb005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;Thirty years had passed, and although he had no real regrets about marrying Wendy, buying a home, and having two kids, Peter found his thoughts often going back to his life in Never-Never-Land.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/24/4</guid><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jul 2026 08:14:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-07-24 #4</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/24/3</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F2c4dc1a0cdd70137c56b005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“You boys got a bottle opener?”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/24/3</guid><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jul 2026 08:13:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-07-24 #3</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/24/2</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2Fcc61ad90e9ef0137cf93005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;The questions were getting harder, and Ted could feel Lucky’s watchful glare from across the room. He had been warned, he recalled, that this was a breed that would sometimes test him.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/24/2</guid><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jul 2026 08:12:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-07-24 #2</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/24/1</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F8726b930e3ad0137cd49005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“‘You have a small capacity for reason, some basic tool-making skills, and the use of a few simple words.’... Yep. That’s you.”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/24/1</guid><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jul 2026 08:11:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-07-24 #1</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/24/0</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F74c80830fa840137d52f005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“Okay. Here’s another little ditty we can all sing. … Of course, as always, the only words are ‘ribbit, ribbit, ribbit.’”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/24/0</guid><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jul 2026 08:10:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-07-23 #5</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/23/4</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F3d498480cdd30137c56b005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“AAAAAAAAAAlbert!”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/23/4</guid><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 08:09:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-07-23 #4</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/23/3</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F9114a380d8ba0137c959005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“Yes! That’s right! The answer is ‘Wisconsin’! Another 50 points for God, and … uh-oh, looks like Norman, our current champion, hasn’t even scored yet.”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/23/3</guid><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 08:08:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-07-23 #3</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/23/2</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2Fcee88000d7410137c8a6005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;Frances loved her little pets and dressed them differently
 every day.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/23/2</guid><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 08:07:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-07-23 #2</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/23/1</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F0298e8b0e9f00137cf93005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“Talk about rubbing it in! Not only did we arrive late, but they deliberately left his organ-donor card.”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/23/1</guid><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 08:06:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-07-23 #1</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/23/0</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F7321b4c0fa840137d52f005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/23/0</guid><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 08:05:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-07-22 #5</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/22/4</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F14a61ba0cdd40137c56b005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/22/4</guid><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 08:04:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-07-22 #4</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/22/3</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F06812040dcca0137caaf005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/22/3</guid><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 08:03:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-07-22 #3</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/22/2</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2Ffac2bd60dcca0137caaf005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;Eventually, Murray took the job—but his friends never did speak to him again.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/22/2</guid><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 08:02:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-07-22 #2</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/22/1</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F7c8536a0e92f0137cf47005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;Zorg dupes the entire tribe in an incident later known as “firegate.”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/22/1</guid><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 08:01:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-07-22 #1</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/22/0</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2Fffdb3a80e6f70137ce50005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“Okay, Frank, that’s enough. … I’m sure the Jeffersons are quite amazed at your car headlight device.”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/22/0</guid><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 08:00:00 -0400</pubDate></item></channel></rss>